3dplot install instructions:

Requirements:
OpenGL 1.2 or greater  - Avaliable from http://www.opengl.org/applications/installing.html
GLUT 3.7 or greater    - Avaliable from http://www.opengl.org/resources/libraries/glut.html
ImageMagick            - Avaliable from http://www.imagemagick.org/

1. Edit Makefile and set PREFIX
2. Run 
	make
3. As root run
	make install

The please consult the man page and README file for usage instructions.

To uninstall 3dplot then, as root, run
make uninstall
